===Verb===     
{{en-infl-reg-other-e|finagl|e|}}

# {{transitive}} To obtain or achieve by [[indirect]], usually [[deceit]]ful methods: ''finagle a day off from work'' 
# {{transitive}} To [[cheat]]; [[swindle]]: ''shady stockbrokers who finagle their clients out of fortunes'' 
# {{intransitive}} To use [[crafty]], deceitful methods.

